-- üßæ ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡πà‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å (‡πÅ‡∏ä‡∏£‡πå‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏´‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á GUI)
local selectedPlayers = {}

-- üåê ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏Ñ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏´‡πá‡∏ô HD Admin
local function sendMessage(command, value)
	local hdAdminClient = ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild("HDAdminClient")
	if not hdAdminClient then
		warn("‚ùå ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö HDAdminClient ‡πÉ‡∏ô ReplicatedStorage")
		return false
	end

	local signals = hdAdminClient:FindFirstChild("Signals")
	if not signals then
		warn("‚ùå ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö Signals ‡πÉ‡∏ô HDAdminClient")
		return false
	end

	local requestCommand = signals:FindFirstChild("RequestCommand")
	if not requestCommand then
		warn("‚ùå ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö RequestCommand ‡πÉ‡∏ô Signals")
		return false
	end

	local args = { ":" .. command .. " " .. value }
	local success, result = pcall(function()
		requestCommand:InvokeServer(unpack(args))
	end)
	if success then
		print("‚úÖ ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á: " .. args[1])
		return true
	else
		warn("‚ùå ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏ß‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£InvokeServer: " .. tostring(result))
		return false
	end
end

-- üñºÔ∏è GUI 1: Player Selector UI
